lease

public Taskqueue.Tasks.Lease lease(String project,
                                   String taskqueue,
                                   Integer numTasks,
                                   Integer leaseSecs)
                            throws IOException
Lease 1 or more tasks from a TaskQueue. Create a request for the method "tasks.lease". This request holds the parameters needed by the the taskqueue server. After setting any optional parameters, call the Taskqueue.Tasks.Lease.execute() method to invoke the remote operation.

Parameters:
project - The project under which the queue lies.
taskqueue - The taskqueue to lease a task from.
numTasks - The number of tasks to lease.
leaseSecs - The lease in seconds.
Returns:
the request
Throws:
IOException - if the initialization of the request fails
